      "name": "Internal flow-field velocity validation via PIV measurements",
      "description": "Simulated velocity magnitude distributions compared against particle image velocimetry (PIV) data at three measurement planes. Qualitative agreement assessed via visual comparison of contour plots and quantitative via L2-norm error metric. Inherent variability in PIV measurements assessed qualitatively based on known seeding density and laser sheet thickness limitations; structured uncertainty quantification link not established for this result.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/morrison/uq/uq-flow-field-aleatory"
