    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 framework. Pressure rise validation MAPE of 4.2% and NIH MAPE of 8.7% both within the 15% acceptance band. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 satisfied at all five operating points. Grid convergence confirmed with GCI < 5% for primary QoIs. The CFD model is assessed as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the defined COU.",
